Logs and remediation reports

Each verifier will create a timestamped run directory.

Stage 2:

/var/log/repoinfra/mailcow-stage2-verify/<timestamp>/

Stage 3:

/var/log/repoinfra/mailcow-stage3-verify/<timestamp>/

Each directory will contain:

